The more I've done

59
00:03:03,517 --> 00:03:06,520
investigative and political
journalism in Puerto Rico,

60
00:03:06,554 --> 00:03:09,223
the more I feel
a responsibility to stay here

61
00:03:09,257 --> 00:03:11,191
and help out my nation.

62
