00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:56,983
There are many layers
to the culture here.

476
00:21:57,016 --> 00:21:59,819
♪

477
00:21:59,852 --> 00:22:01,821
First, of course,
were the Taino,

478
00:22:01,854 --> 00:22:03,990
the indigenous peoples
of the islands,

