50 years of his life,

505
00:23:33,613 --> 00:23:35,247
been perfecting the art

506
00:23:35,281 --> 00:23:38,951
of the perfect slow-roasted
suckling pig.

507
00:23:40,853 --> 00:23:43,490
He starts work at 4:00 a.m.

508
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:51,430
